              <tr> 
                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Advanced Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Legendary Wings</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.48)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=21431">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9014">Ryan "Pisces6996" Mitchell</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9014&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> An Arderian assault that leaves the opponent helpless for an inevitable finish!</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> February 14, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> MAGI:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(898)">Delia</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(336)">Vellup</a>)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(528)">Sorreah</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(670}<a href="javascript:card_browser({528)">Sorreah</a>&#39;s Dream</a>, Any 2 Arderial Spells)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(526)">Aula</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(519)">Brannix</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(521)">J&#39;lith</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(348)">Cloud Sceptre</a>)<br>
<br>
CREATURES: 18 total<br>
3 <a href="javascript:card_browser(339}<a href="javascript:card_browser({337)">Xyx</a> Minor</a><br>
